{"type":"text","timestamp":1775881650902,"sessionID":"ses_2853666dbffeDUJW2TNchl5Tol","part":{"id":"prt_d7acb3f45001rNmsiPoflWljm3","messageID":"msg_d7acb364b001OcXlo4lw21QfP8","sessionID":"ses_2853666dbffeDUJW2TNchl5Tol","type":"text","text":"## AR-018 Archive Summary — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 (Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller)\n\n### What Was Completed\n\n| Component | Status | Details |\n|-----------|--------|---------|\n| **Design Documentation** | ✅ Complete | `design.md` (1236 lines), `delta-spec.md` (316 lines), `tasks.md` (284 lines) |\n| **Reconciler Implementation** | ✅ Complete | `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` (170 lines) |\n| **Unit Tests** | ✅ Complete | `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go` (931 lines, 24 test cases) |\n| **Package Documentation** | ✅ Complete | `pkg/agentd/doc.go` (70 lines with GoDoc) |\n\n**Implementation Highlights:**\n- **Reconciler struct** with `client.Client` and `Scheme *runtime.Scheme` fields\n- **Reconcile method** implementing full idle cleanup algorithm:\n  - Fetches Sandbox resources by namespace/name\n  - Reads `last-activity-time` annotation from workloadmanager\n  - Parses RFC3339 timestamps with error handling (30s requeue on parse error)\n  - Computes expiration time (lastActivity + 15 minutes)\n  - Deletes expired sandboxes with idempotent NotFound handling\n  - Requeues at exact expiration time for non-expired sandboxes\n- **SetupWithManager** method for controller-runtime registration\n- **Constants**: `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`, `RequeueAfterParseError = 30 * time.Second`\n\n**Test Coverage:** 97.0% with 24 test cases covering:\n- Sandbox not found, Get errors\n- Missing/empty annotation handling\n- Invalid timestamp parsing (malformed, empty)\n- Not expired / Just expired / Expired scenarios\n- Delete NotFound idempotency, Delete errors\n- Future expiration requeue calculation\n- Multiple namespaces, edge cases (zero time, far future)\n\n---\n\n### What Was Deferred\n\n| Component | Status | Reason |\n|-----------|--------|--------|\n| **Binary Entry Point** | ❌ Deferred | `cmd/agentd/main.go` NOT implemented |\n| **Integration Tests** | ❌ Deferred | Requires main.go for full integration |\n\n**Deferred Details:**\n- **ST-4.7 Binary Entry Point** — The `cmd/agentd/` directory exists but is **empty**\n  - No `main.go` to create controller-runtime manager\n  - No scheme registration for core Kubernetes + sandbox types\n  - No manager configuration (metrics/health disabled)\n  - No signal handler setup for graceful shutdown\n\n---\n\n### Verification Results\n\n```\n✅ go test ./pkg/agentd/...          PASS (24 tests)\n✅ go test ./pkg/agentd/... -cover   97.0% coverage\n✅ go build ./pkg/agentd/...         Success (no errors)\n❌ go build ./cmd/agentd/...         FAILED (no main.go)\n```\n\n---\n\n### Deliverables Checklist\n\n| Deliverable | Status |\n|-------------|--------|\n| `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` | ✅ Implemented |\n| `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go` | ✅ Implemented (97% coverage) |\n| `pkg/agentd/doc.go` | ✅ Implemented |\n| `cmd/agentd/main.go` | ❌ **Deferred** |\n\n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design) → ST-4.1 through ST-4.6, ST-4.8 (partial) Completed  \n**Next Step:** Implement `cmd/agentd/main.go` to complete ST-4.7 and enable binary build","time":{"start":1775881650899,"end":1775881650899}}}
